\newlabel{fig:gen_basic}{{6}{8}{{\bfseries Basic Generalization Evaluation (MLP-Base).} Success rates of the privileged policy across basic spatial variations including base position, initial/target heights, and object shapes. The policy shows strong geometric invariance but fails at hard spatial boundaries (e.g., height +10cm)}{figure.caption.6}{}}
